    "title": {
        "rendered": "CardBody"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<p><code>CardBody</code> renders an optional content area for a <a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/block-editor/reference-guide/components/card/card/\"><code>Card</code></a>. Multiple <code>CardBody</code> components can be used within <code>Card</code> if needed.</p>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { Card, CardBody } from '@wordpress/components';\n\nconst Example = () =&gt; (\n    &lt;Card&gt;\n        &lt;CardBody&gt;...&lt;/CardBody&gt;\n    &lt;/Card&gt;\n);\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Props</h2>\n<p>Note: This component is connected to <a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/block-editor/reference-guide/components/card/card/#context\"><code>Card</code>&#8216;s Context</a>. The value of the <code>size</code> prop is derived from the <code>Card</code> parent component (if there is one). Setting this prop directly on this component will override any derived values.</p>\n<h3><code>isScrollable</code>: <code>boolean</code></h3>\n<p>Determines if the component is scrollable.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Required: No</li>\n<li>Default: <code>false</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><code>isShady</code>: <code>boolean</code></h3>\n<p>Renders with a light gray background color.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Required: No</li>\n<li>Default: <code>false</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><code>size</code>: <code>string</code></h3>\n<p>Determines the amount of padding within the component.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Required: No</li>\n<li>Default: <code>medium</code></li>\n<li>Allowed values: <code>xSmall</code>, <code>small</code>, <code>medium</code>, <code>large</code></li>\n</ul>\n",
